Simplestone
============

Is a simplified Sandstone project

forked from http://github.com/vigetlabs/sandstone
the simplify it by removing any configurations during installation, just install and run.


Dependencies
============

Requires Rails 2.3 or higher

Required gem installation
  
  - acts_as_versioned
    note: packaged acts_as_versioned has bugs on Rails 2.3 so we will be using the trunk version
    to install the trunk version:

        ./plugin install git://github.com/technoweenie/acts_as_versioned.git

  - acts_as_tree

    gem install acts_as_tree



Installation
=============

./script/plugin install git://github.com/melvinsembrano/simplestone.git

then execute:

rake db:migrate


ENJOY..